dct_title_s: Automobile road from Los Angeles, Cal. to Phoenix, Ariz. via San Bernardino - Brawley - Yuma - Phoenix
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Oriented with north toward upper right.
Shows roads, railroads, waterways, water source quality.
Indicates distances from Los Angeles and Phoenix.
Numbered 188 in lower right, 5 in upper right, and 64 in left margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
